Subject: [PATCH] phy: mscc: Stop taking ts_lock for tx_queue and use its own
 lock
References: bsc#1234429
Patch-mainline: 6.12.46
Git-commit: 9b2bfdbf43adb9929c5ddcdd96efedbf1c88cf53

[ Upstream commit 9b2bfdbf43adb9929c5ddcdd96efedbf1c88cf53 ]

